        </nav>
    </header>

              <div id="score" class="page">
        <section class="hero">
            <h1>Understanding the Wove Score</h1>
            <p>Every product you scan receives a letter grade from A+ to F. Our proprietary algorithm analyzes multiple factors to give you an instant, easy-to-understand sustainability rating.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="grade-cards">
            <div class="grade-card">
                <div class="grade-badge grade-a">A+/A</div>
                <div class="grade-info">
                    <h3>Excellent</h3>
                    <p>Natural fibers, certified sustainable, minimal chemical treatment. Safe for sensitive skin and the environment.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="grade-card">
                <div class="grade-badge grade-b">B/C</div>
                <div class="grade-info">
                    <h3>Good to Moderate</h3>
                    <p>Mixed natural and synthetic fibers with some chemical treatments. Acceptable for most uses but not ideal for sensitive skin.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="grade-card">
                <div class="grade-badge grade-d">D</div>
                <div class="grade-info">
                    <h3>Poor</h3>
                    <p>High synthetic content with chemical treatments. Reduced breathability and increased microplastic concerns.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="grade-card">
                <div class="grade-badge grade-f">F</div>
                <div class="grade-info">
                    <h3>Avoid</h3>
                    <p>Primarily synthetic fabrics. Non-breathable, high microplastic shedding, and significant environmental impact.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="analysis-section">
            <div class="analysis-content">
                <h2>What we Analyze</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Percentage of natural vs. synthetic fibers</li>
                    <li>Third-party certifications (GOTS, OEKO-TEX, RWS, GRS)</li>
                    <li>Chemical treatments and finishes</li>
                    <li>Microplastic shedding risk</li>
                    <li>PFAS and harmful chemical concerns</li>
                    <li>Breathability and skin safety</li>
                    <li>Overall environmental sustainability</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Our detailed scoring methodology is proprietary. Each factor is weighted based on extensive research and industry standards to provide you with the most accurate sustainability assessment.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="analysis-image">
                [Product Score Display]
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="how-it-works">
            <h2>How it Works</h2>
            <p>Three easy steps to shopping consciously</p>
            <div class="steps">
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-icon">⬇</div>
                    <h3>Step 1: Download the Extension</h3>
                    <p>Sign up to get the link to the extension.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-icon">🛒</div>
                    <h3>Step 2: Shop Anywhere</h3>
                    <p>Browse your favorite stores like Amazon, Zara, or Reformation as usual.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-icon">w</div>
                    <h3>Step 3: See the Score</h3>
                    <p>Instantly view the Wove Score, fabric breakdown, and health impacts.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="cta-section">
            <h2>First 100 get 70% off for life.</h2>
            <form class="cta-form">
                <input type="email" placeholder="Email" required>
                <button type="submit">GET EARLY ACCESS</button>
            </form>
        </section>

        <footer>
            <div class="footer-content">
                <p>© 2025 Wove. Shop consciously. Live comfortably.</p>
                <div class="footer-links">
                    <a href="#">About</a>
                    <a href="#">How Scoring Works</a>
                    <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a>
                    <a href="#">Contact</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </footer>
    </div>
